[51]In this campaign, the Flocks suffered a few losses, and during January 1941, the 41st Group was replaced by the 95 th Group of the 35th Squadron.
[52]But it was precisely in this theater of operations that, due to torrential rain, proved to be the weaknesses of the wood structure, which forced to make continuous adjustments and tightening which reduced the efficiency of the aircraft.
[53]JugoslaviaI CANT opened the hostilities against Yugoslavia, 6 April 1941, bombing of the Mostar airport.
[54]During that short invasion, the Regia Aeronautica deployed 49 CANT.
[55]ZBis, 26 of 47º Stormo, 15 of the 95 th Group (the 35th Wing), and eight of the 50th Group (of the 16th Stormo).
